<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM2.10.1">
<l>kiḷaroḷi yiḷamai keṭuvataṉ muṉṉam</l>
<l>vaḷaroḷi māyōṉ maruviya kōyil</l>
<l>vaḷariḷam poḻilcūḻ māliruñ cōlai</l>
<l>taḷarvila rāki cārvatu catirē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before shining bright youth gets lost</l>
<l>it is a blessing to approach, as ones without faintness,</l>
<l>Māliruñcōlai, surrounded by growing young groves,</l>
<l>the temple that is joined by the growing bright Dark one.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
